  "3255590": {
    "name": "Grove Keeper",
    "steam_appid": 3255590,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是林地守护者——一位古老的森林神灵，为捍卫最后一片原始森林免遭人类扩张的侵袭，你苏醒了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个中世纪世界，人类的贪婪正在恣意掠夺森林。伐木者、偷猎者和入侵的军队不断向森林深处推进。为了阻止他们，你必须唤醒大地本身。在这场生死存亡的战略性反击战中，让森林生长、野生动物复苏、指挥强大的守护者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Grove Keeper》是一款实时战略游戏，大自然既是你的武器也是你的资源。随着季节逐一过去，敌人也会越来越强大，你要塑造战场、控制领地、释放毁灭性的自然之力。你的森林越是健康，你的影响力就越大——但当压力加剧时，任何疏忽都可能令你陷入险境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >林地是有生命的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而时间所剩无几。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/db096a4a349a76e3845a1b045ae25b8e.poster.avif?t=1772100330\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/db096a4a349a76e3845a1b045ae25b8e.webm?t=1772100330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/db096a4a349a76e3845a1b045ae25b8e.mp4?t=1772100330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/ae24af0857bef4e519bc864751d8b696.webp?t=1772100330\" width=621 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >野生动物与树木构成了你神力的骨干。当动物回归、生态系统繁荣发展，你与自然的联结就会加强，解锁新的魔法神力与策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >培植树木以产生能量，操控敌军动向，重塑战场格局。小心地进行扩张，守护关键的神力之地，决定大地如何应对入侵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >失去平衡，魔法将会枯萎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加以滋养，森林仍存希望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/31bea1f1eb0a7ae3eeb50292aa13692f.poster.avif?t=1772100330\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/31bea1f1eb0a7ae3eeb50292aa13692f.webm?t=1772100330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/31bea1f1eb0a7ae3eeb50292aa13692f.mp4?t=1772100330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/dbe1450cc592a1620827b1691ab9598e.webp?t=1772100330\" width=621 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >召唤汹涌的洪水冲走入侵者，以闪电撕裂天空，或在混沌中开辟疗愈之地。当一切手段均告失败，亦可召唤古神之力，一旦其苏醒，万物都将灭亡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的魔法与周遭的生灵世界紧密相连。森林越是蓬勃发展，你的神力越强大——但每个法术都需要抉择，每个抉择都会重塑战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/6b19570f08abea19864ea0b017dc602f.poster.avif?t=1772100330\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/6b19570f08abea19864ea0b017dc602f.webm?t=1772100330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/6b19570f08abea19864ea0b017dc602f.mp4?t=1772100330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/85bf08eb125bab2e69e2871279b3fed1.webp?t=1772100330\" width=621 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >召唤并掌控一系列源自北欧、凯尔特及斯拉夫传说的神话生物军团——哥布林、山羊人、高大的巨人等等。每位守护者在战场上各司其职，既有敏捷的远程攻击者，也有凶悍的近战防御者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心配置他们，以你的神力支援他们，将他们部署在最需要的地方。掌握他们的力量，组合他们的能力，并随着新威胁的出现调整你的策略——无论你偏爱防御阵型、积极进攻还是精心策划的反击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/864e6bd89673e5f049184da820b6369e.poster.avif?t=1772100330\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/864e6bd89673e5f049184da820b6369e.webm?t=1772100330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/864e6bd89673e5f049184da820b6369e.mp4?t=1772100330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/0dc73843a8976d13c5271a47c0afa867.webp?t=1772100330\" width=621 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类势力不会罢休。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从卑微的伐木工到重武装的战士和操纵火焰的焚烧者，随着一个个季节过去，你的敌人变得越来越危险。他们不断适应环境、组织团体，逐渐深入森林，所到之处只留下破坏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要生存下去，你必须掌控古老的神力之地，阻挡敌人前进，并把大地本身转化为武器。守住关键地带，瓦解敌人的攻势，坚守森林的最后防线——以免林地永远消失。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/8e97ec860b7c9f1b2b063b0b13a3cc92.poster.avif?t=1772100330\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/8e97ec860b7c9f1b2b063b0b13a3cc92.webm?t=1772100330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/8e97ec860b7c9f1b2b063b0b13a3cc92.mp4?t=1772100330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/aededa783de48a42b292aa1c1083ad4c.webp?t=1772100330\" width=621 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >林地的变化永不停息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从春日宁静的新生到冬季的严酷考验，每个季节都在重塑大地，改变游戏玩法。在春季看似游刃有余的关卡，到了秋冬季节可能变得危险重重，因为资源日渐匮乏，敌人也更加凶猛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在不同季节回到相同地点，难度会随之变化，迫使你制定新策略。某个季节蓬勃生长的物种，在下个季节可能要挣扎求存——通过每轮游玩鼓励你体验新的策略、适应环境，提升游戏的重玩价值。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/4195c585a35cbfef821ceb3e6ae89242.poster.avif?t=1772100330\" width=1170 height=646 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/4195c585a35cbfef821ceb3e6ae89242.webm?t=1772100330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/4195c585a35cbfef821ceb3e6ae89242.mp4?t=1772100330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255590/extras/731e5f7e7a6773a9a8c01f719877d02f.webp?t=1772100330\" width=621 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 跨越四季的21个关卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 不断递增的难度与策略抉择</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 超过15个独特的守护者，各具不同的游戏风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 超过15种随时间发展的敌人类型</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 超过7种强大的自然能力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- RPG风格的成长与升级系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>森林在求助</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是要予以回应……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还是任其烧毁？</p>",
